{"tid":608132,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拍拖性事一問（巴打入）","createTime":"2018-03-28T02:00:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T02:56:28.000Z","uid":44241,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8041c73aeacc1f78be11257526c2e74dbc2e51d2","tid":608132,"uid":44241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T02:00:57.000Z","msg":"好多情侶啱啱開始拍拖都會日夜瘋狂搞嘢 好似搞嘢就是生命 搞嘢就是力量 岀岀入入咁同你度過左好多高高低低起伏咁<br />\n我係絲打 同男朋友一開始都有咁樣嘅時候 而呢個階段好正常好快咁亦都漸漸無左 我都明白果種一開頭嘅新鮮同熱情 <br />\n有睇過我啲po嘅會知道我同男友關係一向都麻麻地<br />\n甚至可以用唔健康嘅關係黎形容 間唔中會有一點點嘅好轉 會有一瞬間覺得佢變左暖男咁<br />\n過左一開頭個階段之後 通常都係我提出先會做果樣嘢 我好奇嘅一樣嘢係 最近佢竟然會主動提出 而且比平時我地搞嘢嘅時間更加頻密 <br />\n好想知佢諗咩 有咩因素情況下會咁？有冇經驗人可以解答我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c6d1ced6119adcc8f6774c008015314b369c7e","tid":608132,"uid":36187,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T02:02:11.000Z","msg":"冇錢叫雞姐"},{"pid":"3badb5249f8c4290313b48997a4e828a24abda39","tid":608132,"uid":138138,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T02:02:29.000Z","msg":"入錯黎，出番去先，，。<br />\n畢竟我係絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ce0d4cd62d182d257b7bb436fc1b12da279b2f","tid":608132,"uid":169662,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T02:03:11.000Z","msg":"你 只不過係一隻有體溫既飛機杯"},{"pid":"54124d4cfe92a8d6a9d5b0b313106a8e99211b43","tid":608132,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55c6d1ced6119adcc8f6774c008015314b369c7e","tid":608132,"uid":36187,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T02:02:11.000Z","msg":"冇錢叫雞姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T02:03:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"104339a2d8281b3691f7bebed317b4deec4a4dd1","tid":608132,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T02:04:37.000Z","msg":"免費雞"},{"pid":"09a